| [http://www.2getthere.eu/ 2getthere]&lt;ref name=&quot;mogge1&quot;&gt;Mogge, John, ''[http://faculty.washington.edu/jbs/itrans/moggeprtpaper.pdf The Technology of Personal Transit],'' &quot;Figure 6. MASDAR Phase 1A Prototype Passenger PRT.&quot; Paper delivered at the [http://www.worldfutureenergysummit.com World Future Energy Summit], January 20, 2009. Available in WFES online media center.&lt;/ref&gt;
